    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vector Wave</strong> is a chaotic retro-themed party game strongly focused on physics-based action. Vector Wave brings you back to the basics - health does not exist, instead you must blast your opponents out of bounds by scavenging for weapons in the arena. Last one standing wins! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218500/extras/5d63ed3207b85194f703bec123a5975c.poster.avif?t=1771447719\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218500/extras/5d63ed3207b85194f703bec123a5975c.webm?t=1771447719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218500/extras/5d63ed3207b85194f703bec123a5975c.mp4?t=1771447719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ONLINE AND LOCAL MULTIPLAYER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into Vector Wave with friends, a game that supports 2-4 player online and local multiplayer! Battle against friends by organising a chaotic free-for-all, or test your cooperative skills by teaming up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNIQUE WEAPONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With access to 50+ weapons in Vector Wave, there will always be something perfect for you to knock your opponents away! Each weapon has its own unique feel, ranging from a throwable rock perfect for disarming your enemies to a rare but intimidating launcher harnessing the power of a black hole! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218500/extras/dd7c247174f53af7eee451ff67ddf05d.poster.avif?t=1771447719\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218500/extras/dd7c247174f53af7eee451ff67ddf05d.webm?t=1771447719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218500/extras/dd7c247174f53af7eee451ff67ddf05d.mp4?t=1771447719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't want guns? Explode your way to victory with grenades like impacts, frags and clusters! Or maybe control the arena by rigging the map with automated turrets, life-ending landmines and... skateboarding ducks? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218500/extras/5770fe4164a00536532ce4deb69c3355.poster.avif?t=1771447719\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218500/extras/5770fe4164a00536532ce4deb69c3355.webm?t=1771447719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218500/extras/5770fe4164a00536532ce4deb69c3355.mp4?t=1771447719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CUSTOMISE YOUR EXPERIENCE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you like self-expression and the latest square-based fashion trends? We've got you covered! Choose 1 of 8 neon colours to determine your team, and customize your square with 60+ unlockable hats to flaunt and impress your friends! Playing games and winning rounds will net you some shiny Vector Tokens to spend in the hat shop. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>When the dust settles, only one square can be left standing...</i></strong></p>",
